author: @DevG-rp8uf
text: Nice concept.....but it's good to remember that following fate is sensible only for those with good luck at that moment. Several had fate pull them in negative direction by having situations arranged thus. When everything came together for something wrong to happen,sometimes you have the choice to say yes or no to it. If you keep silent and go along with whatever is happening, however the current flows, good or bad, will come to you. Its better to use one's intelligence in all circumstances and consider if something is good for one, thinking of every aspect. Trusting fate is not always sensible. Even God might only be able to speak through a person who gives soft suggestion. Once a step is taken, perhaps nothing can help. So using one's own intelligence, would be more sensible than blindly following fate. All the best girls❤

author: @ogaetbabybeel1025
text:
IVE has zero flops under his belt 😎!! 

I can't wait to discover the rest of the film concept for "Attitude" 😱🥰!! Personally, I am won over by this concept and I still think I took the best flight 🥰🔥!!
 Around me, I only heard "Blackpink, Stray Kids or BTS", they are excellent groups, there is no photo, but I wanted something to stand out 🤔😁.

 I have the same concept with Manga, music. Obviously I started with big names, but today, I tell myself that if I were in the place of this or that group or Mangakas, I would like to be given a chance 🔥❤️!!

 I can only wish the best for this new year to my favorite K-Pop group, each member, each girl who is part of it, a huge congratulations for your talent, for knowing how to stand out and thank you very much for your hard work, for the passion you put into it 🙇🏻. 


Let's do our best in 2025 and surpass ourselves!!
